istent with the previous results on 4U 1735-44 and several black hole X-ray\nbinaries that anti-correlations are observed during the transition states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2013 05:45:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
