ined from $\\nu(t)$ or $\\dot\\nu(t)$. Finally, the uncertainty\nin the starting time $t_0$ of a classical glitch causes uncertainties to some\nglitch parameters, but less so to a slow glitch and $t_0$ of which can be\ndetermined from data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2013 14:54:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-12"}
